    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid value for anyone seeking a dependable daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are sound and perform reliably under normal driving conditions. However, please be aware that there are some visible signs of wear, including minor cosmetic scratches on the exterior and some interior upholstery aging. It may also require routine maintenance soon, such as a brake pad replacement or a suspension tune-up, to keep it running smoothly. Overall, it's a functional, honest car that gets the job done without any major surprises.",
